  "description": [
    "CROWDS HURTING FOR LUKE SANDERS Noose Will Play a Part Before Quiet is Restored HOUSTON SANDERS CAUGHT Claims He Took No Part in tlie Skoot iugJokn Sanders Is Yet Alive Conspiracy to Kill Mullen Marion April 9SpecialOfficers and citizens have been starching the country for tho past fortyeight hours for Luke Sanders one of the negroes implicated in the killing of Muilen the road overseer on Thursday Houston Sanders was captured Friday night Houston says he made no effort to escape and that he had no pistol and took ho part in tho shooting The inquest was begun Friday evening before Justice Clif ton Johnston and as a result of the inves tigation thus far twenty negroes are now in jail Excitement lias not abated in the least and tho community in which the kill ing occurred is up in arms and serious trouble is expected every hour Tho Sanders family is large and it Is thought they are shielding Luke The cor oners investigation has developed beyond question that a conspiracy was planned to kill Mullen and as the case proceeds tho more hienous the case appears John Sanders reported dead is yet alive and lingering in the county"
  ],
